  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Specific mental functions related to the awareness of one's identity, one's body, one's position in the reality of one's environment and of time.
Inclusions: functions of experience of self, body image and time</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni mentali specifiche correlate alla consapevolezza della propria identitÃƒ , del proprio corpo, della propria posizione nella realtÃƒ  del proprio ambiente e temporale.

Inclusione: funzioni dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢esperienza del sÃƒÂ©, dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢immagine corporea e del tempo</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢esperienza del sÃƒÂ© e del tempo</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Experience of self and time functions</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b189">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni mentali specifiche, altro specificato e non specificato</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Specific mental functions, other specified and unspecified</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Stroke"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Traumatic_Brain_Injury"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Vocational_Rehabilitation"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Hearing_Loss"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Stroke"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Traumatic_Brain_Injury"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Vocational_Rehabilitation"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Hearing_Loss"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sensory functions relating to sensing the presence of light and sensing the form, size, shape and colour of the visual stimuli.
Inclusions: visual acuity functions; visual field functions; quality of vision; functions of sensing light and colour, visual acuity of distant and near vision, monocular and binocular vision; visual picture quality; impairments such as myopia, hypermetropia, astigmatism, hemianopia, colour-blindness, tunnel vision, central and peripheral scotoma, diplopia, night blindness and impaired adaptability to light
Exclusions: perceptual functions (b156)</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni sensoriali relative alla percezione della presenza della luce e dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢aspetto, dimensione, forma e colore degli stimoli visivi.

Inclusioni: funzioni dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢acuitÃƒ  visiva; funzioni del campo visivo; qualitÃƒ  della visione; funzioni relative alla percezione della luce e del colore, acuitÃƒ  visiva della visione da lontano e da vicino, visione monoculare e binoculare; qualitÃƒ  dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢immagine visiva; menomazioni come miopia, ipermetropia, astigmatismo,
emianopsia, cecitÃƒ  ai colori, visione a tunnel, scotoma centrale e periferico, diplopia, nictalopia e ridotta adattabilitÃƒ  alla luce

Esclusione: funzioni percettive (b156)</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni della vista</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing form and contour, both binocular and monocular, for both distant and near vision.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Visual acuity functions</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21000">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21000"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing size, form and contour using both eyes for objects distant from the eye.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Binocular acuity of distant vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21001">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21001"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing size, form and contour using either right or left eye alone, for objects distant from the eye.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Monocular acuity of distant vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21002">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21002"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing size, form and contour, using both eyes, for objects close to the eye.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Binocular acuity of near vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21003">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21003"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2100"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing size, form and contour, using either right or left eye alone, for objects close to the eye.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Monocular acuity of near vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2101">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2101"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions related to the entire area that can be seen with fixation of gaze.
Inclusions: impairments such as in scotoma, tunnel vision, anopsia</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Visual field functions</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b210"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions involving light sensitivity, colour vision, contrast sensitivity and the overall quality of the picture.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Quality of vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21020">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21020"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of sensing a minimum amount of light (light minimum), and the minimum difference in intensity (light difference).
Inclusions: functions of dark adaptation; impairments such as night blindness (hyposensitivity to light) and photophobia (hypersensitivity to light)</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Light sensitivity</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21021">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21021"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of differentiating and matching colours.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Colour vision</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21022">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21022"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions of separating figure from ground, involving the minimum amount of luminance required.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Contrast sensitivity</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21023">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21023"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Seeing functions involving the quality of the picture.
Inclusions: impairments such as in seeing stray lights; affected picture quality (floaters or webbing); picture distortion, and seeing stars or flashes</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Visual picture quality</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b21028">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b2102"/>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Quality of vision, other specified</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b215">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Stroke"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Traumatic_Brain_Injury"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b215"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Stroke"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Traumatic_Brain_Injury"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Functions of structures in and around the eye that facilitate seeing functions.
Inclusions: functions of internal muscles of the eye, eyelid, external muscles of the eye, including voluntary and tracking movements and fixation of the eye, lachrymal glands, accommodation, pupillary reflex; impairments such as in nystagmus, xerophthalmia and ptosis
Exclusions: seeing functions (b210); Chapter 7 Neuromusculoskeletal and Movement-related Functions (b7)</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni delle strutture interne e attorno allÃ¢â‚¬â„¢occhio che facilitano le funzioni della vista.

Inclusioni: funzioni dei muscoli interni dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢occhio, della palpebra, dei muscoli esterni dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢occhio, inclusi i movimenti volontari e di rilevamento, e aggiustamento dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢occhio, ghiandole lacrimali, accomodazione, riflesso pupillare; menomazioni come nel nistagmo, xeroftalmia e ptosi

Esclusioni: funzioni della vista (b210); Capitolo 7 Ã¢â‚¬â€œ Funzioni
neuro-muscoloscheletriche e correlate al movimento</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni delle strutture adiacenti allÃ¢â‚¬â„¢occhio</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Functions of structures adjoining the eye</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b230">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Vocational_Rehabilitation"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual"/>
