  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sensation of unpleasant feeling indicating potential or actual damage to some body structure felt in either one or both upper limbs, including hands.</ICF-:description>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Pain in upper limb</rdfs:label>
