  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Body_functions"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Spinal_Cord_Injury"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Muskoloskeletal_Conditions_for_Post_Acute_Care"/>
  <ICF-:description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Functions of inhaling air into the lungs, the exchange of gases between air and blood, and exhaling air.
Inclusions: functions of respiration rate, rhythm and depth; impairments such as apnoea, hyperventilation, irregular respiration, paradoxical respiration, and bronchial spasm, and as in pulmonary emphysema; reduction in airflow through upper and lower airways
Exclusions: respiratory muscle functions (b445); additional respiratory functions (b450); exercise tolerance functions (b455)</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni di inalazione di aria nei polmoni, lo scambio di gas tra aria e sangue e lÃ¢â‚¬â„¢esalazione dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢aria.

Inclusioni: funzioni di frequenza, ritmo e profonditÃƒ  di respirazione; menomazioni come apnea, iperventilazione, respirazione irregolare, respiro paradosso e spasmo bronchiale, e come nellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢enfisema polmonare

Esclusioni: funzioni del muscolo respiratorio (b445); ulteriori funzioni respiratorie (b450); funzioni di tolleranza dellÃ¢â‚¬â„¢esercizio fisico (b455)</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Funzioni respiratorie</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Respiration functions</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#b445">
