  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Muskoloskeletal_Conditions_for_Post_Acute_Care"/>
  <ICF-:description xml:lang="en">Raising up an object or taking something from one place to another, such as when lifting a cup or toy or carrying a box, or a child from one room to another.

Inclusions: lifting, carrying in the hands or arms, or on shoulders, hip, back, or head; putting down</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sollevare un oggetto o portare un oggetto da un posto allÃ¢â‚¬â„¢altro, come prendere in mano una tazza o portare un bambino da una stanza a unÃ¢â‚¬â„¢altra.

Inclusioni: sollevare, portare in mano o sulle braccia, o sulle spalle, sul fianco, sulla schiena o sulla testa; mettere giÃƒÂ¹</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sollevare e trasportare oggetti</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Lifting and carrying objects</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

<owl:Class rdf:about="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#d440">
  <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Activities_and_participation"/>
