  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#d610"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Activities_and_participation"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Spinal_Cord_Injury"/>
  <ICF-:description xml:lang="en">Buying, renting, furnishing and arranging a room, house, apartment or other dwelling.

Inclusions: buying or renting a place to live and furnishing a place to live

Exclusions: acquisition of goods and services (d620); caring for household objects (d650)</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Comprare, prendere in affitto, arredare e sistemare una casa, un appartamento o un altro alloggio.

Inclusioni: comprare o prendere in affitto un posto in cui vivere e arredarlo

Esclusioni: procurarsi beni e servizi (d620); prendersi cura degli oggetti della casa (d650)</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Procurarsi un posto in cui vivere</ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Acquiring a place to live</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

