  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Activities_and_participation"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Spinal_Cord_Injury"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Stroke"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/ICF-exc-coreset#Traumatic_Brain_Injury"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Hearing_Loss"/>
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.stiima.cnr.it/RientraOnt3Merged#Low_Back_Pain"/>
  <ICF-:description xml:lang="en">Engaging in aspects of community social life, such as engaging in charitable organizations, services clubs or professional social organizations.

Inclusions: informal and formal associations; ceremonies

Exclusions: non-remunerative employment (d855); recreation and leisure (d920); religion and spirituality (d930); political life and citizenship (d950)</ICF-:description>
  <ICF-:descrizioneITA rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Impegnarsi in tutti gli aspetti della vita sociale della comunitÃƒ , come impegnarsi in organizzazioni caritatevoli, circoli o organizzazioni sociali professionali.

Inclusioni: associazioni informali e formali; cerimonie Esclusioni: lavoro non retribuito (d855); ricreazione e tempo libero (d920); religione e spiritualitÃƒ  (d930); vita politica e cittadinanza (d950)</ICF-:descrizioneITA>
  <ICF-:nomeIta rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Vita nella comunitÃƒ </ICF-:nomeIta>
  <rdfs:label rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Community life</rdfs:label>
</owl:Class>

