  <JobL:ONet_short_description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Landscape or maintain grounds of property using hand or power tools or equipment. Workers typically perform a variety of tasks, which may include any combination of the following: sod laying, mowing, trimming, planting, watering, fertilizing, digging, raking, sprinkler installation, and installation of mortarless segmental concrete masonry wall units.</JobL:ONet_short_description>
