  <JobL:ONet_job_titles rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Sample of reported job titles: Bulk Mail Technician, Clerk, Distribution Clerk, Part Time Flexible Clerk (PTF Clerk), Postal Clerk, Sales &amp; Service Associate (SSA), Sales and Distribution Clerk, Sales and Service Associate (SSA), Window Clerk, Window/Distribution Clerk</JobL:ONet_job_titles>
  <JobL:ONet_short_description rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Perform any combination of tasks in a post office, such as receive letters and parcels; sell postage and revenue stamps, postal cards, and stamped envelopes; fill out and sell money orders; place mail in pigeon holes of mail rack or in bags; and examine mail for correct postage.</JobL:ONet_short_description>
